author: Shee XinPing
text: India should also develop Portable Nuclear reactors which could be assembled in space stations and can be used on future Spacecrafts, if we want formidable Space program. And for all this we should start the development today then we will be able to produce these reactors in 2050. These Reactors will also help us in Defense sector. Nuclear can be most compact portable energy source possible.

author: Shee XinPing
text: why are we not going for Nuclear reactors. we should be producing 30-40% of our energy needs through Nuclear. More safer technologies are available now a days. APR 1000 is already there. I dont think we should be able to meet our demands with renewable only if want to replace as much Crude as possible. Also nuclear take large time to build and are mostly more costly than renewable and coal. We also need to build huge Public transport infra running on electricity like metro and rail in all the tier 2 and metros.
